{"tid":1678691,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"棄用奧斯爾 艾馬利：係全隊決定","createTime":"2019-10-27T18:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T19:22:26.000Z","uid":205785,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f2604065b789da8a9dee787df144980ca4f6ede7","tid":1678691,"uid":205785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:46:17.000Z","msg":"艾馬利上季接手雲格的工作，開始阿仙奴的領隊生涯，同時間也是奧斯爾噩夢的開始。雖然奧斯爾的質素，明顯比格列沙加、古安杜斯等球員為佳，但這名世界盃冠軍成員，始終都得不到艾帥歡心，相信於短時間內，都沒可能搶得正選位置。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n艾帥表示：「事實上，我曾和球員們作出傾談，彼此達成了一個協議。我們作為一個團隊、一個整體，大家要合作就要坦誠相對，之後才可以取得成績。之前我們就共同商議了暫時不讓奧斯爾出場的決定。我知球迷都希望知道原委，但現時並不是公開談話的時候。」(<a href=\"http://goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoal.com&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4RPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=452c37c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goal.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/hk.sports.yahoo.com/amphtml/news/%25E6%25A3%2584%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E6%2596%25AF%25E7%2588%25BE-%25E8%2589%25BE%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%2588%25A9-%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%259A%258A%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A-121104361.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fhk.sports.yahoo.com%2Famphtml%2Fnews%2F%2525E6%2525A3%252584%2525E7%252594%2525A8%2525E5%2525A5%2525A7%2525E6%252596%2525AF%2525E7%252588%2525BE-%2525E8%252589%2525BE%2525E9%2525A6%2525AC%2525E5%252588%2525A9-%2525E4%2525BF%252582%2525E5%252585%2525A8%2525E9%25259A%25258A%2525E6%2525B1%2525BA%2525E5%2525AE%25259A-121104361.html&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4RPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=4cbf7677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/hk.sports.yahoo.com/amphtml/news/%25E6%25A3%2584%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E6%2596%25AF%25E7%2588%25BE-%25E8%2589%25BE%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%2588%25A9-%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%259A%258A%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A-121104361.html</a>"},{"pid":"7169d9259c4e092ad5930e85dd919bac63adefb5","tid":1678691,"uid":205785,"lik